FBIS4-48186 "drafr094_a_94012" FBIS-AFR-94-094 Daily Report 14 May 1994 CENTRAL AFRICA Rwanda Fresh Fighting in Kigali Fresh Fighting in Kigali LD1405103494 Paris France-Inter Radio Network in French 1000 GMT 14 May 94 LD1405103494 Paris France-Inter Radio Network French BFN [Text] Fresh fighting with heavy weapons is reported in Kigali, the Rwandan capital. The toll of victims is rising. Between 100,000 and 200,000 are reported to have died. The rebel forces have claimed to be in control of nearly half of the country after five weeks of fighting.
